#: ../../../release/dev/swift-ninja-separate-swiftmodule-edge.rst:2
msgid "swift-ninja-separate-swiftmodule-edge"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release/dev/swift-ninja-separate-swiftmodule-edge.rst:4
msgid ""
"The :ref:`Ninja Generators` gained the :prop_tgt:"
"`Swift_SEPARATE_MODULE_EMISSION` target property, initialized by the :"
"variable:`CMAKE_Swift_SEPARATE_MODULE_EMISSION` variable, to control whether "
"importable Swift targets emit ``.swiftmodule`` from a dedicated build edge.  "
"Policy :policy:`CMP0215` enables this by default."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release/dev/swift-ninja-separate-swiftmodule-edge.rst:10
msgid ""
"The default :prop_tgt:`Swift_MODULE_NAME` now replaces hyphens with "
"underscores, since hyphens are not valid in Swift module identifiers."
msgstr ""
